snippet.textDisplay:
say :
3× Allahumma inni as'aluka al-jannah
3×Allahumma Ajirni Minan Naar

Say:ALHAMDULLILAH ×33
SUBHANALLAH x33
Allahu akbar ×33
Astagfirullahx33
Take time 4 dikhr & for you and I to earn good deeds


Recite "Allahummaghfirlil muslimeen wal muslimaat, wal mu'mineen wal mu'minat, Al-ahyaa minhum wal amwaat"
Ameen

Say Wa La Hawla Walaa quwata illah billah then say: La illaha illallah lastly say: Allahu Akbar. And your minor sins should be erased Inshallah
